  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "UNP is going to celebrate its birthday in a big way",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The United National Party 76th anniversary is scheduled to be held at Sugathadasa Stadium in Colombo on September 06 under the theme \"Ekwemu\".",
        "The anniversary convention will be held under the chairmanship of the UNP leader, President Ranil Wickramasinghe.",
        "The United National Party is holding this year's conference under a president of the party after 28 years. They held an anniversary conference in 1993 under a United National Party President. After that, a party anniversary will be held under a president this year."
      ],
